    panda_impedance.xml
    Derived from: ../../simulation/tactile_sensor/mjcf_check/franka_emika_panda/panda_20260405.xml

    Actuator change: position-scaled -> direct torque control
      Original:  gainprm="500"  ctrlrange="-2.8973 2.8973"  (ctrl in rad-scale, force = 500*ctrl)
      This file: gainprm="1"    ctrlrange="-87 87"           (ctrl in Nm directly)

    Arm joints 1-7: ctrl [Nm] -> torque [Nm] with gain=1, no position/velocity feedback
    Gripper (actuator8): unchanged, remains position-controlled (PD on tendon "split")

    Mesh assets: resolved via relative path to original asset directory.
    See README.md in this directory for path setup details.
  -->
